--- Orbitali Status --- * KeyValueCollection fixed * removed unused code

--- Orbitali Status --- * Conposer json updated * Website updated with resouces route

--- Orbitali Status --- * Updated migrations for unique fields * Added Model structure for Base Model * Added Status scope * Website controller added some functions * Models linked base model * added fillWithExtra method * KeyValueModel fixed for eager loading * Website views updated

--- Orbitali Status --- * Added casting to extras * Updated preCreate method and added Status scope * Orbitali convert to json implements Arrayable, Jsonable, \JsonSerializable * Orbitali loader updated if not active website or node goto 404 * Adding casting options in models * Extras value is nullable
--- Orbitali Status --- * Form migration updated * NodeTrait fixed for codacy * Added form post trait Add FormSubmission in class
--- Orbitali Status --- * Added redirect type for url
--- Orbitali Status --- * User migration updated for laravel * added default language and country inside panel * Node and Structure controller added * form render added * relationFinder added
